# Code Size (API)

Soft limits on `src/` — split in same PR when exceeded.

| Vượt ~200 | Tách |
|-----------|------|
| Action | Private methods; sync → trait; large orchestration → Service |
| Query | Filter/sort/include concerns |
| Service | One use-case per class |
| Request / Resource | Child classes or nested resources |

| Vượt ~20 method | Tách |
|-----------------|------|
| create/update | `transformPayload()`, `syncRelations()` |

Extract: `.cursor/extracts/http-layer.md` for layer boundaries.
